&lt;li&gt;Full benefits package including health, dental, vision, 401k and paid time-off&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Laptop computer provided after virtual training completed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work from home&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
